```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ§© Object Methods

Objects can store **functions** as values.

```js
let user = {
  name: "Saakshi",
  greet: function () {
    console.log("Hello " + this.name);
  }
};

user.greet();
```

ğŸ“Œ `this` refers to the current object

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ” Looping Through Objects

forâ€¦in Loop

```js
for (let key in user) {
  console.log(key, user[key]);
}
```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ“¦ Object Built-in Methods

