---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ§  Nested Objects

Objects inside objects.

```js
let student = {
  name: "Amit",
  marks: {
    math: 90,
    science: 85
  }
};
```

Access:

```js
student.marks.math;
```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ“š Array of Objects (Very Important â­)

Used in real applications.

```js
let users = [
  { name: "A", age: 20 },
  { name: "B", age: 22 }
];
```

Access:

```js
users[0].name;
```

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ§© Object Destructuring

Extract values easily.

```js
